4%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.0.46.</span> <span class="nav-text">说明 BS与CS 的联系，还有区别。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#forward-%E5%92%8Credirect%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.0.47.</span> <span class="nav-text">forward 和redirect的区别？</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#cookie-%E5%92%8C-session-%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.0.48.</span> <span class="nav-text">cookie 和 session 的区别？</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></div>
